{"sections":{"section_hero_KRyVzB":{"type":"section-hero","blocks":{"heading_xYf7ei":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"ARE CHEAP ENGAGEMENT RINGS BAD?","heading_font_size":"heading-small","heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["heading_xYf7ei"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/b947f53c-ffa4-4255-ad3c-081031bb10ab.jpg","link":"","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","flex_align_desktop":"align--bottom-right-desktop","content_width":50,"mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/toolxox.com-final-tcmfBQ6leU_89d1a906-6853-4a12-ab90-1668ee66b69a.jpg","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","flex_align_mobile":"align--bottom-right-mobile","color_scheme":"scheme-2","show_text_background":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","show_title":true,"heading_font_size":"heading-large","show_content":true,"text_font_size":"body-medium","align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":50,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_text_with_products_ki6d6b":{"type":"section-text-with-products","settings":{"subheading":"","heading":"Breaking the Myths About Engagement Rings: Affordable Options Are Just As Perfect!","width":"wrapper","text_font_size_px_desktop":27,"text_align_desktop":"text-center","text_font_size_px_mobile":22,"text_align_mobile":"text-center--mobile","color_scheme":"scheme-6","padding_top":32,"padding_bottom":32}},"section_double_slider_JyrqLk":{"type":"section-double-slider","blocks":{"text_slide_bmnk9n":{"type":"text-slide","settings":{"subheading":"","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-large","text":"<p>It’s easy to assume that engagement rings have to come with a hefty price tag, thanks to the longstanding \"three months' salary\" tradition. However, you don’t have to follow this norm to have a meaningful engagement. Choosing a more affordable ring doesn't mean compromising on quality or significance. In fact, it could even bring you closer as a couple. Let’s explore why opting for an affordable engagement ring might be the best decision you can make.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_slide_bmnk9n"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Who_Buys_the_Man_s_Wedding_Band.webp","image_width":"one-half","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":4,"text_alignment":"text-left","layout":"","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_announcement_cFDXfp":{"type":"section-announcement","blocks":{"text_wcEdHC":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_font_size":"body-small","color":"","target_device_enabled":false,"target_device":"mobile"}}},"block_order":["text_wcEdHC"],"settings":{"slider_speed":7,"text_alignment":"center","marquee_speed":100,"direction":"ticker-rtl","message_spacing":10,"show_border":false,"layout":"marquee","color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_double_slider_G4dWiN":{"type":"section-double-slider","blocks":{"text_slide_jMPFPC":{"type":"text-slide","settings":{"subheading":"","title":"Breaking Free from the Diamond Standard","heading_font_size":"heading-large","text":"<p>Since the 1930s, diamond giants like De Beers have convinced us that diamonds are a must-have for engagement rings. Their iconic \"A Diamond is Forever\" slogan has fueled the idea that only expensive diamonds can symbolize everlasting love. But what you may not know is that this idea was largely driven by marketing, and it’s not necessarily true.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_slide_jMPFPC"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/unique_affordable_wedding_rings_why_shop.webp","image_width":"one-half","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":4,"text_alignment":"text-left","layout":"is-reversed","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_announcement_98QA3c":{"type":"section-announcement","blocks":{"text_wEHRfX":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_font_size":"body-small","color":"","target_device_enabled":false,"target_device":"mobile"}}},"block_order":["text_wEHRfX"],"settings":{"slider_speed":7,"text_alignment":"center","marquee_speed":100,"direction":"ticker-rtl","message_spacing":10,"show_border":false,"layout":"marquee","color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_double_slider_jXX4cA":{"type":"section-double-slider","blocks":{"text_slide_Xk84UU":{"type":"text-slide","settings":{"subheading":"","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-large","text":"<p>De Beers and other big names in the diamond industry created several myths that many people still believe today, such as the misconception that diamonds are a great investment or that they’re rare. In reality, diamonds lose a significant portion of their value the moment you walk out of the store, and they are far more common than you might think. So, why are they so expensive? It’s all down to clever advertising.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_slide_Xk84UU"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/O_1200PX_15752356_M_1_720x_83e6cff7-6f76-43ae-a7e2-be5584431838.webp","image_width":"one-half","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":4,"text_alignment":"text-left","layout":"","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_announcement_ygUKPY":{"type":"section-announcement","blocks":{"text_WTTrAM":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_font_size":"body-small","color":"","target_device_enabled":false,"target_device":"mobile"}}},"block_order":["text_WTTrAM"],"settings":{"slider_speed":7,"text_alignment":"center","marquee_speed":100,"direction":"ticker-rtl","message_spacing":10,"show_border":false,"layout":"marquee","color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_double_slider_t4VAG3":{"type":"section-double-slider","blocks":{"text_slide_JwHBjt":{"type":"text-slide","settings":{"subheading":"","title":"Why Consider Affordable Engagement Rings?","heading_font_size":"heading-large","text":"<p>Now that we’ve debunked the myth that expensive diamond rings are the only option, let’s talk about the incredible advantages of choosing a more affordable engagement ring. Don’t be fooled — these rings can be just as stunning and meaningful, and they often come with some significant perks.<br\/><br\/>Affordable Rings Could Strengthen Your Relationship While diamonds are pretty, they’re also overrated. In fact, research has shown that couples who spend more on engagement rings have a higher likelihood of getting divorced. It’s no surprise — entering a marriage with debt or financial stress from an expensive ring isn’t the ideal foundation for a lasting relationship.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"Affordable Engagement Rings","button_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/engagement-ring","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_slide_JwHBjt"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/why-us-image-5_87310d65-6bb0-4c52-9df4-c4a6bd8ac9e7.webp","image_width":"one-half","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":4,"text_alignment":"text-left","layout":"is-reversed","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_announcement_CTMedY":{"type":"section-announcement","blocks":{"text_e6jeJQ":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_font_size":"body-small","color":"","target_device_enabled":false,"target_device":"mobile"}}},"block_order":["text_e6jeJQ"],"settings":{"slider_speed":7,"text_alignment":"center","marquee_speed":100,"direction":"ticker-rtl","message_spacing":10,"show_border":false,"layout":"marquee","color_scheme":"scheme-3","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_double_slider_eW4pzG":{"type":"section-double-slider","blocks":{"text_slide_qKa9eB":{"type":"text-slide","settings":{"subheading":"","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-large","text":"<p>Many affordable rings are crafted from high-quality materials and are just as beautiful as their expensive counterparts. Whether you prefer a simulated diamond or a vintage heirloom, these options are durable, long-lasting, and could even be passed down to future generations.<br\/><br\/>Affordable Doesn’t Mean Cheap Affordable engagement rings don’t have to mean low quality. If you adore the sparkle of diamonds, you can opt for handcrafted simulated diamonds. These stones are carefully crafted for brilliance, cut, clarity, and color, ensuring they look as dazzling as natural diamonds — at a fraction of the cost. Plus, they’re conflict-free, making them an ethical choice.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"","button_url":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["text_slide_qKa9eB"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/womens-ring.webp","image_width":"one-half","autoplay":true,"a